tiers.ability_description: Whenever Dark Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.

The first time each Hutt Cartel ally falls below 50% Health, they gain Damage Immunity for 1 turn, which can't be copied, dispelled, or prevented.\n\nWhenever an enemy takes damage from a Thermal Detonator expiring, Hutt Cartel allies recover 5% Health and Protection, gain 5% Turn Meter, and there is a 50% chance that enemy is inflicted with a Thermal Detonator for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled, prevented, or resisted.

The max cooldown of Inventive is reduced by 1. Whenever Boushh inflicts Thermal Detonators on an enemy, inflict an additional Thermal Detonator for 2 turns and Hutt Cartel allies gain 10% Armor Penetration (max 70%) and 10% Turn Meter (once per turn).
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
Whenever a Scoundrel ally defeats an enemy, they take a bonus turn.
Whenever Dark Side allies grant a buff to another ally, that other ally recovers 3% Health and Protection.
Whenever Light Side allies grant a buff to another ally, that other ally recovers 3% Health and Protection.
Whenever a Scoundrel ally deals damage to an enemy and no other enemy is Ability Blocked, inflict Ability Block for 1 turn on the enemy, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.
Whenever an enemy loses Turn Meter, Empire allies gain Protection Up (stacking, 10%) for 2 turns.  Whenever an ally loses Protection Up they gain 10% Turn Meter.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.
Whenever Empire allies critically hit an enemy during their turn, that ally gains 10% Offense (stacking) for 2 turns.
The first time each Dark Side ally reaches 90%, 70%, and 50% Health inflict Doubt on a random enemy that doesn't have it for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled or prevented.
